The Sims 4: City Living (c) Electronic Arts

12/2016 :..... RELEASE.DATE .. PROTECTION .......: Origin + DLC
     1 :.......... DISC(S) .. GAME.TYPE ........: Sims

Do your Sims long to leave the suburbs behind? Fulfill their dreams in the
diverse city of San Myshuno, where they can discover exciting neighborhoods,
move into a new apartment, check out fun festivals and more. In The Sims 4
City Living your Sims can experience the joys and challenges of sharing
close quarters with other Sims. Work your way up from a starter unit to a
penthouse as your Sims launch new metropolitan careers!

Note:

This is the full game, v1.25.136.1020, including the City Living expansion
pack, the Vintage Glamour stuff pack, as well as all the previous updates
and stuff/game/expansion packs.

Release was hidden in an INTERNAL stocking because you're not supposed to
unrar your presents before Christmas Eve 

Have a "merry christmas" and enjoy !

TEAM HOHOHO 2016
